name: Black Catopus
description:
Before Europeans taught you that Black cats were bad luck, she was a goddess in ancient Kemet/Egypt by the name of Bastet, black cats were known for keeping evil spirits away.

I make not-so-traditional mandalas. Each one has a very specific energy and intention put into it. You can use it as a wallpaper on your screen or print it out and hang it on your wall and it will have effect on your psyche.
